title: Any ongoing scheme under Regulation 33(7) which fulfills the criteria under this Regulation can be included in the proposal under Regulation 33 (9) for approval or converted into a CDS under this Regulation 33(9)
clause_text: Any ongoing scheme under Regulation 33(7) which fulfills the criteria under this Regulation can be included in the proposal under Regulation 33 (9) for approval or converted into a CDS under this Regulation 33(9). However, all dilutions of reservations under Regulation 33(7) shall have to be restored as per this Regulation.
